Here is the **same cloud-security architecture diagram recreated in Mermaid**, fully compatible with GitHub, GitLab, Obsidian, MkDocs, and VS Code Markdown preview.

This is a **flowchart-style secure CI/CD â†’ ECR â†’ EKS/ECS** architecture with scanning, signing, IAM, and network controls.

